a site use flask
show a graph of one weibo's reposts

prepare on mac:
1, mongodb
2, ruby <(curl -fsSkL raw.github.com/mxcl/homebrew/go) (install brew)
3, brew install libevent
4, sudo easy_install gevent
5, sudo easy_install pymongo
6, sudo easy_install Flask-PyMongo
7, sudo easy_install simplejson
8, git clone git@github.com:MOON-CLJ/pygexf.git
9, sudo python setup.py install
10, sudo easy_install lxml
11, python simple.py
